{"1":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.25","c":"وَيْلٌ","d":"wyَlٌْ","e":"waylun"},{"b":"0.82","h":"1.12","c":"لِكُلِّ","d":"lkِّlُِّ","e":"likulli"},{"b":"1.8","h":"2.7","c":"هُمَزَةٍ","d":"hmُzَẗٍَ","e":"humazatin"},{"b":"2.8","h":"4.12","c":"لُمَزَةٍ","d":"lmُّzَẗٍَ","e":"lumazatin"}],"a":{"g":"Woe to every scorner and mocker","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                وقال تعالى \"ويل لكل همزة لمزة\" قيل الهمزة: النمام. وقال مجاهد أنه قال في \"ويل لكل همزة لمزة\" الهمزة: الطعان في الناس، واللمزة: الذي يأكل لحوم الناس.\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, the Most High has said, \"Woe to every slanderer [humaza], backbiter [lumaza].\" It is said: The slanderer [humaza] is the talebearer [nammam]. And Mujahid said regarding \"Woe to every slanderer [humaza], backbiter [lumaza]\": The slanderer [humaza] is the one who disparages people, and the backbiter [lumaza] is the one who consumes the flesh of people.\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.65","c":"الَّذِي","d":"lٱdَّhàِ","e":"alladhī"},{"b":"1.0","h":"2.21","c":"جَمَعَ","d":"gjmَعَʿَ","e":"jamaʿa"},{"b":"1.8","h":"3.26","c":"مَالًا","d":"māَlāً","e":"mālan"},{"b":"2.5","h":"4.32","c":"وَعَدَّدَهُ","d":"wعَʿdَdَّhَۥُ","e":"waʿaddadahu"}],"a":{"g":"Who collects wealth and [continuously] counts it."}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.06","h":"0.5","c":"يَحْسَبُ","d":"yḥَsْbَُ","e":"yaḥsabu"},{"b":"0.92","h":"1.79","c":"أَنَّ","d":"ʾanََّ","e":"anna"},{"b":"2.3","h":"3.08","c":"مَالَهُ","d":"māَlhَۥُٓ","e":"mālahu"},{"b":"4.8","h":"5.62","c":"أَخْلَدَهُ","d":"ʾakَhlْdَhَۥُ","e":"akhladahu"}],"a":{"g":"He thinks that his wealth will make him immortal."}},"4":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.7","c":"كَلَّا","d":"klَāَّ","e":"kallā"},{"b":"1.6","h":"3.25","c":"لَيُنْبَذَنَّ","d":"lyَnُbۢdَhnََّ","e":"layunbadhanna"},{"b":"4.8","h":"6.14","c":"فِي","d":"fàِ","e":"fī"},{"b":"5.0","h":"6.58","c":"الْحُطَمَةِ","d":"lٱḥْṭُmَẗَِ","e":"l-ḥuṭamati"}],"a":{"g":"No! He will surely be thrown into the Crusher."}},"5":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.35","c":"وَمَا","d":"wmَāَٓ","e":"wamā"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.44","c":"أَدْرَاكَ","d":"ʾadَrْàَkَٰ","e":"adrāka"},{"b":"3.0","h":"4.31","c":"مَا","d":"māَ","e":"mā"},{"b":"3.2","h":"4.62","c":"الْحُطَمَةُ","d":"lٱḥْṭُmَẗَُ","e":"l-ḥuṭamatu"}],"a":{"g":"And what can make you know what is the Crusher?"}},"6":{"w":[{"b":"0.05","h":"0.9","c":"نَارُ","d":"nāَrُ","e":"nāru"},{"b":"0.67","h":"2.09","c":"اللَّهِ","d":"lٱlhَِّ","e":"l-lahi"},{"b":"1.6","h":"3.57","c":"الْمُوقَدَةُ","d":"lٱmْwُqdَẗَُ","e":"l-mūqadatu"}],"a":{"g":"It is the fire of Allah, [eternally] fueled,"}},"7":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.06","c":"الَّتِي","d":"lٱtَّàِ","e":"allatī"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.78","c":"تَطَّلِعُ","d":"tṭَlَّعِʿُ","e":"taṭṭaliʿu"},{"b":"2.0","h":"3.61","c":"عَلَى","d":"عʿlَàَ","e":"ʿalā"},{"b":"2.5","h":"4.42","c":"الْأَفْئِدَةِ","d":"lٱʾْafَـْdِٔẗَِ","e":"l-afidati"}],"a":{"g":"Which mounts directed at the hearts."}},"8":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.15","c":"إِنَّهَا","d":"ʾinِhَّāَ","e":"innahā"},{"b":"1.8","h":"2.23","c":"عَلَيْهِمْ","d":"عʿlَyَhْmِ","e":"ʿalayhim"},{"b":"2.8","h":"4.63","c":"مُؤْصَدَةٌ","d":"mʾُّwṣْdَẗٌَ","e":"mu'ṣadatun"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, Hellfire will be closed down upon them"}},"9":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.3","c":"فِي","d":"fàِ","e":"fī"},{"b":"0.37","h":"0.82","c":"عَمَدٍ","d":"عʿmَdٍَ","e":"ʿamadin"},{"b":"2.4","h":"3.05","c":"مُمَدَّدَةٍ","d":"mmُّdَdَّẗٍَۭ","e":"mumaddadatin"}],"a":{"g":"In extended columns."}}}